                    <a href="images/posts/te-anau-and-milford-sound/te-anau--milford-sound-25_8541822462_o-large.jpg" class="fancybox">
                        <img src="images/posts/te-anau-and-milford-sound/te-anau--milford-sound-25_8541822462_o.jpg"/>
                    </a>

                    <p>On the way back to the dock, we sailed very close to one of the waterfalls, and rainjackets were handed out for the brave souls who wanted to stand out the front of the boat as we did this! I had my camera with me, and after the fiasco I had with dropping it in the water in Australia, there was no way I was going to risk it getting wet again!</p>

                    <a href="images/posts/te-anau-and-milford-sound/te-anau--milford-sound-19_8540703853_o-large.jpg" class="fancybox">
                        <img src="images/posts/te-anau-and-milford-sound/te-anau--milford-sound-19_8540703853_o.jpg"/>
                    </a>

                    <p>The boat moored up, and we all streamed off and back onto the bus, to continue our journey through to Queenstown.</p>

